00:19:54,420 --> 00:19:56,700
Were the bodies moved last night?

411
00:19:58,100 --> 00:19:58,940
Last night?

412
00:19:59,260 --> 00:20:00,140
What happened last night?

413
00:20:00,500 --> 00:20:01,340
Nothing.

