454
00:22:36,660 --> 00:22:38,060
Long Dan, keep searching!

455
00:22:38,060 --> 00:22:38,900
Yes.

456
00:22:39,620 --> 00:22:40,460
Er'niu.

457
00:22:47,860 --> 00:22:50,220
Mr. Zhen, don't go too far.

458
00:22:50,420 --> 00:22:51,660
I can't stand you

459
00:22:51,660 --> 00:22:52,980
