00:23:36,820 --> 00:23:37,660
Yu Qi,

475
00:23:37,820 --> 00:23:38,740
don't be reckless.

476
00:23:54,900 --> 00:23:56,100
- Move it.
- Yes.

477
00:24:01,940 --> 00:24:03,100
- Watch it.
- Yes.

478
00:24:05,260 --> 00:24:06,100
Chief!

479
00:24:06,620 --> 00:24:08,020
Chief, we've found the bodies.

480
00:24:29,580 --> 00:24:31,220
Bodies! Bodies!

481
00:24:31,220 --> 00:24:32,060
