482
00:24:33,500 --> 00:24:35,340
Take Cao Xingyu, the suspect,

483
00:24:35,460 --> 00:24:37,220
back to the Capital Security Office.

484
00:24:37,220 --> 00:24:38,300
- Yes.
- Wait.

485
00:24:39,180 --> 00:24:40,580
