Confess to it.

505
00:25:30,740 --> 00:25:33,500
We've treated you well.

506
00:25:34,060 --> 00:25:35,860
We've arranged your marriage

507
00:25:36,340 --> 00:25:37,380
and secured your lineage.

508
00:25:38,100 --> 00:25:39,020
Cao Xingyu,

509
00:25:41,060 --> 00:25:42,540
stop threatening him.

510
00:25:44,020 --> 00:25:46,140
Anzi, don't be afraid.

511
00:25:46,700 --> 00:25:47,940
Tell us everything.

512
00:25:48,900 --> 00:25:50,940
This case spans too wide to ignore.

513
00:25:51,210 --> 00:25:52,460
I can report it directly to His Majesty.

514
00:25:53,820 --> 00:25:55,620
No matter their rank,

515
00:25:56,260 --> 00:25:58,180
