520
00:26:13,500 --> 00:26:14,780
You know

521
00:26:15,540 --> 00:26:17,260
my character and strength.

522
00:26:17,380 --> 00:26:19,300
If you confess to your crime,

523
00:26:19,900 --> 00:26:21,220
I can guarantee

524
00:26:21,420 --> 00:26:22,940
that your family won't be implicated.

525
00:26:23,740 --> 00:26:24,580
Understand?

526
00:26:33,220 --> 00:26:34,060
Yes.

527
00:26:35,220 --> 00:26:36,260
I killed them.

528
00:26:37,700 --> 00:26:39,180
