533
00:26:48,260 --> 00:26:49,740
I'm the murderer.

534
00:26:51,740 --> 00:26:53,060
I was blinded by lust

535
00:26:53,060 --> 00:26:54,020
and gave in to my desires.

536
00:26:54,020 --> 00:26:56,060
I killed those girls with my own hands

537
00:26:56,780 --> 00:26:59,100
and threw their bodies into the dry well.

538
00:26:59,340 --> 00:27:01,180
It has nothing to do

539
00:27:02,020 --> 00:27:03,300
with Young Master.

540
00:27:09,380 --> 00:27:10,220
Master,

541
00:27:10,340 --> 00:27:11,980
I beg you to treat my family kindly.

542
00:27:12,100 --> 00:27:12,940
Master!

543
00:27:13,060 --> 00:27:14,780
I'm glad

544
00:27:15,380 --> 00:27:16,820
you admitted your guilt.

545
00:27:17,300 --> 00:27:18,140
Don't worry.

546
00:27:18,540 --> 00:27:20,660
I will treat your family well.

547
00:27:27,020 --> 00:27:27,900
Marquis Changxing,

548
00:27:28,100 --> 00:27:29,620
