551
00:27:35,020 --> 00:27:36,180
Now that

552
00:27:36,180 --> 00:27:38,140
a wicked servant

553
00:27:38,140 --> 00:27:39,860
tarnished Marquis Changxing's reputation,

554
00:27:40,180 --> 00:27:41,540
isn't it better for me

555
00:27:41,540 --> 00:27:42,500
to execute him

556
00:27:42,500 --> 00:27:43,340
on your behalf?

557
00:27:43,580 --> 00:27:45,780
