00:28:34,020 --> 00:28:35,620
You, I!

582
00:28:39,100 --> 00:28:40,780
I'm sorry to bother you.

583
00:28:41,340 --> 00:28:43,220
Do as you please, sir.

584
00:28:45,220 --> 00:28:46,860
Suit yourselves.

585
00:28:47,700 --> 00:28:49,530
I have military affairs to attend to

586
00:28:49,550 --> 00:28:50,940
and don't have the mood

587
00:28:50,940 --> 00:28:52,660
to waste time with you.

588
00:29:09,100 --> 00:29:09,980
Stop looking.

589
00:29:10,420 --> 00:29:11,260
Go back.

590
00:29:13,500 --> 00:29:15,020
Why did you stop me?

591
00:29:15,380 --> 00:29:16,740
Are you going to let them go?

592
00:29:16,740 --> 00:29:17,820
We're here not to prosecute Cao Yong

593
00:29:17,820 --> 00:29:20,020
for killing his servant,

594
00:29:20,020 --> 00:29:21,780
but to find these bodies.

595
00:29:21,780 --> 00:29:23,380
The bodies are all here,

596
00:29:23,380 --> 00:29:24,460
not a single one missing.

597
00:29:24,940 --> 00:29:26,580
But the evidence died with them.

598
00:29:26,580 --> 00:29:28,340
I won't let that happen.

599
00:29:30,740 --> 00:29:32,100
Who's been getting to you?

600
00:29:32,100 --> 00:29:33,020
You're all jittery

601
00:29:33,020 --> 00:29:34,180
out of nowhere.

602
00:29:35,060 --> 00:29:36,140
You are rather young.

603
00:29:36,860 --> 00:29:38,660
Does it have anything to do

604
00:29:39,180 --> 00:29:40,500
with being young?

605
00:29:46,100 --> 00:29:47,260
The servant

606
00:29:47,820 --> 00:29:49,340
didn't kill the girls.

607
00:29:49,740 --> 00:29:51,180
He didn't have the guts.

608
00:29:51,380 --> 00:29:52,380
Was it Qian?

609
00:29:52,980 --> 00:29:54,740
No, Cao Xingyu killed them.

610
00:29:54,980 --> 00:29:56,300
You're not too stupid.

611
00:29:56,300 --> 00:29:57,460
Did you know it all along?

612
00:29:58,020 --> 00:29:59,220
Why didn't you warn me?

613
00:29:59,220 --> 00:30:00,210
How could I warn you?

614
00:30:00,210 --> 00:30:01,340
You kept calling him brother-in-law

615
00:30:01,340 --> 00:30:02,580
intimately.

616
00:30:02,580 --> 00:30:04,020
Would you listen if I warned you?

617
00:30:04,380 --> 00:30:05,740
Cao Xingyu was so cruel

618
00:30:05,740 --> 00:30:06,900
and killed so many people.

619
00:30:08,100 --> 00:30:09,780
Does Qian know about this?

620
00:30:10,180 --> 00:30:11,500
She knows too?

621
00:30:11,900 --> 00:30:13,660
Why did she still invite us over?

622
00:30:13,820 --> 00:30:15,300
How could she do this to me?

623
00:30:15,540 --> 00:30:16,940
Though we weren't born of the same mother,

624
00:30:17,100 --> 00:30:18,460
I'm the closest to her.

625
00:30:21,300 --> 00:30:22,500
Who told you to let Jiang Si go?

626
00:30:28,180 --> 00:30:29,820
After seeing so many dead women,

627
00:30:31,140 --> 00:30:32,540
they were so scared that they asked

628
00:30:32,540 --> 00:30:33,860
the Capital Security to take them out.

629
00:30:34,620 --> 00:30:36,420
How could I stop them?

630
00:30:38,060 --> 00:30:40,540
How dare you talk back to me, wench!

631
00:30:41,180 --> 00:30:43,700
How dare you?

632
00:30:44,500 --> 00:30:45,580
If my mother

633
00:30:45,700 --> 00:30:47,340
weren't happy with you,

634
00:30:47,700 --> 00:30:48,740
I'd kill you

635
00:30:48,910 --> 00:30:49,780
like I killed

636
00:30:49,780 --> 00:30:50,660
those filthy women.

637
00:30:50,780 --> 00:30:52,620
Worthless wench!

638
00:30:52,860 --> 00:30:53,700
Young Master.

639
00:30:54,180 --> 00:30:55,020
Young Master,

640
00:30:55,540 --> 00:30:56,820
for your mother's sake...

641
00:30:57,020 --> 00:30:57,860
Go!

642
00:31:00,980 --> 00:31:02,780
Hit me! Kill me!

643
00:31:03,500 --> 00:31:05,460
Besides hitting and killing women,

644
00:31:05,580 --> 00:31:07,340
what else do you have the guts to do?

645
00:31:08,020 --> 00:31:10,300
Your dad hit you, so you take it out on me.

646
00:31:10,580 --> 00:31:11,460
If you're so tough,

647
00:31:11,460 --> 00:31:12,300
why don't you dare

648
00:31:12,300 --> 00:31:14,060
make a peep in front of him?

649
00:31:23,820 --> 00:31:25,860
As a lowly woman from a humble family,

650
00:31:26,340 --> 00:31:27,900
how dare you look down on me?

651
00:31:28,460 --> 00:31:30,820
Where's the eagerness you had when you

652
00:31:31,060 --> 00:31:32,700
took your cousin's place to marry me?

653
00:31:34,460 --> 00:31:35,740
You brought this

654
00:31:36,860 --> 00:31:38,540
on yourself.

655
00:31:49,100 --> 00:31:49,940
Yes,

656
00:31:50,980 --> 00:31:52,100
I did it.

657
00:31:52,860 --> 00:31:53,900
I deserve it.

658
00:31:54,700 --> 00:31:56,300
Go ahead, kill me!

659
00:31:57,740 --> 00:31:59,140
Give the Capital Security

660
00:31:59,140 --> 00:32:00,180
another body to handle.

661
00:32:01,740 --> 00:32:03,060
Let's see if you'll find another Anzi

662
00:32:03,060 --> 00:32:04,420
to pin it on.

663
00:32:28,300 --> 00:32:30,060
I'll kill you!

664
00:32:41,660 --> 00:32:43,340
I will kill you!

665
00:33:06,780 --> 00:33:08,460
I'll spare you today.

666
00:33:09,620 --> 00:33:11,220
When things calm down,

667
00:33:12,420 --> 00:33:13,860
I'll come back for your cheap life.

668
00:33:20,380 --> 00:33:21,260
Ma'am.

669
00:33:22,260 --> 00:33:23,100
Ma'am.

670
00:33:23,660 --> 00:33:24,540
Ma'am,

671
00:33:26,100 --> 00:33:27,340
are you alright?

672
00:33:31,940 --> 00:33:32,780
Cui'er,

673
00:33:36,220 --> 00:33:37,580
I don't want

674
00:33:40,140 --> 00:33:42,940
to spend another day like this.

675
00:33:47,380 --> 00:33:48,220
Ma'am,

676
00:33:48,820 --> 00:33:49,820
let's run away.

677
00:33:52,180 --> 00:33:53,020
Run?

678
00:33:56,660 --> 00:33:57,980
Where to?

679
00:34:01,380 --> 00:34:03,220
When Miss Si left, she told me

680
00:34:03,580 --> 00:34:05,300
she left a small palanquin

681
00:34:05,300 --> 00:34:06,500
in the alley at the back door

682
00:34:06,900 --> 00:34:08,420
in case you want to go home.

683
00:34:09,180 --> 00:34:10,580
If you don't go,

684
00:34:10,980 --> 00:34:12,860
I'm afraid you'll die.

685
00:34:25,940 --> 00:34:26,780
Ma'am.

686
00:34:27,340 --> 00:34:29,180
I can't just sit around waiting to die.

687
00:34:31,860 --> 00:34:32,700
Go home.

688
00:34:35,340 --> 00:34:36,580
Let's go home.

689
00:34:40,100 --> 00:34:41,020
Go home.

690
00:34:50,660 --> 00:34:53,460
(Morning Drizzle)

691
00:34:53,460 --> 00:34:54,660
(Haitang Chamber)

692
00:34:54,820 --> 00:34:56,020
Heaven must be blind

693
00:34:56,140 --> 00:34:57,100
to let that murderous demon

694
00:34:57,100 --> 00:34:58,220
walk free.

695
00:35:00,220 --> 00:35:01,220
Commandant Yu

696
00:35:01,220 --> 00:35:02,300
vowed to keep digging,

697
00:35:02,540 --> 00:35:04,620
but it's a dead end with the witnesses dead.

698
00:35:04,940 --> 00:35:06,380
I don't think so.

699
00:35:06,540 --> 00:35:08,020
Have you forgotten Miss Chi?

700
00:35:08,180 --> 00:35:10,060
She was so grateful when you asked me

701
00:35:10,060 --> 00:35:11,100
to send her out of town.

702
00:35:11,300 --> 00:35:12,700
Just say the word,

703
00:35:12,700 --> 00:35:13,980
and she'll come testify.

704
00:35:15,940 --> 00:35:17,500
But her life has been so hard,

705
00:35:17,660 --> 00:35:19,060
and she barely managed to escape.

706
00:35:19,300 --> 00:35:20,220
If I ask her

707
00:35:20,220 --> 00:35:21,500
to identify Cao Xingyu,

708
00:35:21,660 --> 00:35:23,300
her days of detention

709
00:35:23,300 --> 00:35:24,380
will become public.

710
00:35:24,820 --> 00:35:25,860
How can a young woman

711
00:35:25,860 --> 00:35:27,220
survive such a thing?

712
00:35:27,540 --> 00:35:28,620
Wouldn't that

713
00:35:28,620 --> 00:35:29,940
push her back to the edge?

714
00:35:30,100 --> 00:35:31,660
If she doesn't testify,

715
00:35:31,660 --> 00:35:33,060
the criminal will walk free.

716
00:35:33,060 --> 00:35:34,540
Do you think she can live in peace?

717
00:35:35,660 --> 00:35:37,100
I'll visit her tomorrow.

718
00:35:38,740 --> 00:35:39,860
Si.

719
00:35:40,820 --> 00:35:42,300
- Si.
- At this hour?

720
00:35:42,300 --> 00:35:43,620
Is she here to make trouble?

721
00:35:43,620 --> 00:35:44,460
Go and take a look.

722
00:35:47,500 --> 00:35:49,140
Miss Pei, what are you doing?

723
00:35:50,820 --> 00:35:52,420
- Si.
- What's up?

724
00:35:52,420 --> 00:35:53,260
Qian,

725
00:35:53,860 --> 00:35:54,860
Jiang Qian is home.

726
00:35:54,860 --> 00:35:56,020
She's at Grandma's now.

727
00:35:58,060 --> 00:35:59,780
(Cixin Hall)

728
00:36:03,380 --> 00:36:04,380
Qian,

729
00:36:04,380 --> 00:36:06,340
stop crying.

730
00:36:07,340 --> 00:36:08,420
You need to tell Grandma

731
00:36:08,420 --> 00:36:10,060
why you ran back home

732
00:36:10,060 --> 00:36:11,460
in the middle of the night?

733
00:36:11,860 --> 00:36:13,060
Rumors say there was a murder

734
00:36:13,340 --> 00:36:15,620
at Marquis Changxing's Mansion.

735
00:36:15,620 --> 00:36:17,180
Several people died.

736
00:36:17,180 --> 00:36:18,980
That's a murder case!

737
00:36:18,980 --> 00:36:20,420
Has your husband been implicated?

738
00:36:20,420 --> 00:36:22,500
Did something happen to him?

739
00:36:22,500 --> 00:36:24,660
With a father who rules the roost,

740
00:36:25,540 --> 00:36:27,140
what's a murder case to him?

741
00:36:27,780 --> 00:36:29,500
Whatever the mess, his father will fix it.

742
00:36:29,620 --> 00:36:31,340
I'm not criticizing you,

743
00:36:31,660 --> 00:36:33,620
but you're husband and wife.

744
00:36:33,820 --> 00:36:35,540
You should share honor and disgrace.

745
00:36:35,860 --> 00:36:38,020
Running back whenever you have a problem

746
00:36:38,340 --> 00:36:39,340
isn't good.

747
00:36:39,340 --> 00:36:40,860
Tell Mother what's wrong.

748
00:36:41,260 --> 00:36:43,100
Did you have a fight with your husband

749
00:36:43,300 --> 00:36:45,140
or did he bully you?

750
00:36:45,660 --> 00:36:46,740
Physical fights

751
00:36:46,740 --> 00:36:49,420
between couples are common.

752
00:36:49,420 --> 00:36:50,540
Ask your mother.

753
00:36:50,740 --> 00:36:52,180
Now that you're married,

754
00:36:52,380 --> 00:36:54,500
you can't be so headstrong.

755
00:36:55,380 --> 00:36:56,660
It's late tonight.

756
00:36:56,660 --> 00:36:57,700
You can stay here.

757
00:36:57,900 --> 00:36:59,740
Go home and apologize

758
00:36:59,740 --> 00:37:01,260
to your husband's family tomorrow morning.

759
00:37:01,260 --> 00:37:03,900
Tell them that Grandma was sick

760
00:37:03,900 --> 00:37:05,300
and called you back tonight.

761
00:37:06,380 --> 00:37:07,260
Qian,

762
00:37:07,420 --> 00:37:08,860
now that you've made it back,

763
00:37:08,860 --> 00:37:10,300
you should tell them everything.

764
00:37:10,300 --> 00:37:11,500
Yes, Qian.

765
00:37:11,500 --> 00:37:12,420
You knew that mansion

766
00:37:12,420 --> 00:37:13,500
was a den of wolves,

767
00:37:13,500 --> 00:37:15,340
yet you dragged your sisters into its jaws.

768
00:37:15,340 --> 00:37:16,540
What's your scheme?

769
00:37:16,740 --> 00:37:18,060
With Grandma here,

770
00:37:18,060 --> 00:37:19,340
lay it all out now.

771
00:37:19,340 --> 00:37:20,180
Shut your mouth!

772
00:37:20,180 --> 00:37:21,660
Den of wolves?

773
00:37:21,820 --> 00:37:22,980
Who gave you the right to speak?

774
00:37:23,100 --> 00:37:25,180
Qiao, tell Grandma

775
00:37:25,180 --> 00:37:26,540
what's going on.

776
00:37:26,740 --> 00:37:27,780
It's Cao Xingyu.

777
00:37:28,140 --> 00:37:29,860
He harbors ill intentions toward Si.

778
00:37:30,380 --> 00:37:31,220
What?

779
00:37:31,420 --> 00:37:34,460
He harbors ill intentions toward Si?

780
00:37:34,740 --> 00:37:35,580
What...

781
00:37:36,020 --> 00:37:38,300
What an enormous joke!

782
00:37:38,580 --> 00:37:39,740
What kind of girl

783
00:37:39,740 --> 00:37:40,620
hasn't he seen?

784
00:37:40,740 --> 00:37:41,980
You, you, and you,

785
00:37:41,980 --> 00:37:43,100
go back now.

786
00:37:43,260 --> 00:37:44,980
Mrs. Li, take them back to their rooms.

787
00:37:45,860 --> 00:37:47,780
Ladies, please return.

788
00:37:53,860 --> 00:37:56,380
Qian, stop crying.

789
00:37:56,380 --> 00:37:58,940
Were you kept in the dark,

790
00:37:58,940 --> 00:38:01,380
so you ran back in anger?

791
00:38:02,420 --> 00:38:03,780
I know everything.

792
00:38:04,060 --> 00:38:05,620
What are you talking about?

793
00:38:05,940 --> 00:38:07,380
What do you mean?

794
00:38:13,860 --> 00:38:14,700
This...

795
00:38:20,580 --> 00:38:21,420
My goodness!

796
00:38:22,020 --> 00:38:25,100
Qian, did he hit you?

797
00:38:25,100 --> 00:38:27,620
He hit you so hard.

798
00:38:27,620 --> 00:38:30,460
Why didn't you tell us earlier?

799
00:38:30,460 --> 00:38:31,460
Tell you?

800
00:38:33,220 --> 00:38:34,740
How could I?

801
00:38:35,820 --> 00:38:37,540
Mother taught me since childhood

802
00:38:38,060 --> 00:38:39,540
and Grandma reminded me day and night

803
00:38:40,250 --> 00:38:41,220
that I'm the finest young lady

804
00:38:41,220 --> 00:38:42,500
in this family.

805
00:38:43,980 --> 00:38:45,540
Our family's fate

806
00:38:45,540 --> 00:38:46,940
rests entirely on me.

807
00:38:47,780 --> 00:38:50,700
I've been studying the four arts

808
00:38:51,140 --> 00:38:52,420
and household management since young,

809
00:38:52,940 --> 00:38:54,340
never slacking for a moment,

810
00:38:55,860 --> 00:38:57,820
all to marry into a marquis's family

811
00:38:58,660 --> 00:38:59,700
and secure a prosperous future

812
00:38:59,700 --> 00:39:01,300
for myself and our family.

813
00:39:01,580 --> 00:39:02,580
But what happened?

814
00:39:02,940 --> 00:39:03,780
I did everything

815
00:39:03,780 --> 00:39:05,180
you said.

816
00:39:05,460 --> 00:39:06,460
Why have I ended up

817
00:39:06,460 --> 00:39:07,700
in this situation?

818
00:39:07,700 --> 00:39:09,740
What did I do wrong?

819
00:39:13,420 --> 00:39:16,180
Four years,

820
00:39:17,100 --> 00:39:18,060
two months,

821
00:39:18,300 --> 00:39:19,460
and seven days married to Cao Xingyu,

822
00:39:21,020 --> 00:39:23,220
every day a living hell.

823
00:39:24,660 --> 00:39:25,580
Fists,

824
00:39:26,380 --> 00:39:27,220
slaps,

825
00:39:27,740 --> 00:39:28,580
whips,

826
00:39:29,500 --> 00:39:31,020
I've tasted them all.

827
00:39:32,060 --> 00:39:32,940
I begged him,

828
00:39:33,820 --> 00:39:34,660
but it was useless.

829
00:39:35,660 --> 00:39:37,060
Then, I tried to fight back,

830
00:39:38,620 --> 00:39:40,500
but that only made him beat me harder.

831
00:39:43,820 --> 00:39:44,980
After enough beatings,

832
00:39:46,580 --> 00:39:47,620
I learned

833
00:39:47,620 --> 00:39:48,460
the most useful trick.

834
00:39:49,340 --> 00:39:50,980
I would play dead

835
00:39:51,340 --> 00:39:52,220
and let him hit a corpse

836
00:39:52,220 --> 00:39:53,580
that gave him nothing.

837
00:39:55,060 --> 00:39:55,980
The more numb I was,

838
00:39:56,700 --> 00:39:58,020
the faster he got bored.

839
00:39:58,980 --> 00:40:00,060
Soon enough,

840
00:40:00,900 --> 00:40:02,740
he would move on to some new fun.

841
00:40:12,260 --> 00:40:13,100
Qian.

842
00:40:14,300 --> 00:40:15,220
Qian, don't be afraid.

843
00:40:15,460 --> 00:40:17,820
Mother will take you back now

844
00:40:18,300 --> 00:40:19,420
to seek a divorce from him.

845
00:40:19,420 --> 00:40:20,260
Nonsense!

846
00:40:21,180 --> 00:40:22,100
If I hadn't come,

847
00:40:22,100 --> 00:40:23,740
you would've turned the place upside down.

848
00:40:23,980 --> 00:40:24,820
Mother,

849
00:40:25,340 --> 00:40:26,780
why didn't you stop them?

850
00:40:26,780 --> 00:40:28,460
How could you let them do this?

851
00:40:28,620 --> 00:40:29,740
Look how

852
00:40:29,740 --> 00:40:31,020
she's been beaten!

853
00:40:31,700 --> 00:40:33,580
Darling, you're finally back.

854
00:40:33,580 --> 00:40:36,420
Take a look at our daughter!

855
00:40:37,180 --> 00:40:38,140
There are bruises

856
00:40:38,140 --> 00:40:40,500
all over her body.

857
00:40:40,500 --> 00:40:42,980
Isn't there justice under the sky?

858
00:40:42,980 --> 00:40:43,820
Tomorrow morning,

859
00:40:43,980 --> 00:40:46,180
we'll go to Marquis Changxing's Mansion

860
00:40:46,180 --> 00:40:47,580
to divorce him!

861
00:40:50,140 --> 00:40:51,740
They really have no regard for the law.

862
00:40:52,300 --> 00:40:53,940
Tomorrow, I'll go to Marquis Changxing

863
00:40:53,940 --> 00:40:54,780
to demand an explanation.

864
00:40:55,180 --> 00:40:56,140
I'll ask him

865
00:40:56,140 --> 00:40:57,220
why his good-for-nothing son

866
00:40:57,540 --> 00:40:59,140
bullied my Qian

867
00:40:59,140 --> 00:41:00,140
like this.

868
00:41:00,380 --> 00:41:01,660
Son, you're right.

869
00:41:01,780 --> 00:41:02,780
They can't

870
00:41:02,780 --> 00:41:04,860
bully Qian anymore.

871
00:41:05,860 --> 00:41:08,300
We have to handle this properly

872
00:41:09,500 --> 00:41:12,060
